briefdescription.para: Entry Point for cFE Table Services Core Application.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This is the entry point to the cFE Table Services Core Application. This Application provides the ground interface to the cFE Table Services.

briefdescription.para: cFE Table Services Core Application Initialization

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function initializes all data associated with the cFE Table Services Core Application. It is only called when the Application is first started.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Processes messages obtained from the command pipe.

parameterdescription.para: a pointer to the message received from the command pipe

briefdescription.para: Compares message with CFE_TBL_CmdHandlerTbl to identify the message.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Searches the Command Handler Table for an entry matching the message ID and, if necessary, the Command Code. If an entry is not located, an error code is returned.

parameterdescription.para: message ID of command message received on command pipe
